Previously an integer was provided to specify the target person to be
edited. The new code changes that functionality to use the full name of
the target person instead. The full name provided as argument is not
required to be case sensitive.

commitResults.messageBody:
This commit introduces the necessary parsers and logic for the schedule add and schedule delete command.

These commands provide users with the ability to manage events effectively within the application, enhancing its functionality and usability.
